videos.headline: Tonges dives for pylon on Cal's opening TD
videos.description: Chase Garbers finds Jake Tonges who lunges for the pylon giving Cal the early lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tonges dives for pylon on Cal's opening TD) 2021/10/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon's Johnny Johnson makes incredible diving catch
videos.description: Johnny Johnson III gets Oregon in Cal territory after making the sensational diving catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oregon's Johnny Johnson makes incredible diving catch) 2021/10/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon loses ball in red zone as Cal recovers a fumble
videos.description: Cal's Elijah Hicks rips the ball away from Kris Hutson and Trey Paster recovers as the Ducks can't score in the red zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oregon loses ball in red zone as Cal recovers a fumble) 2021/10/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Travis Dye breaks through the hole for the Oregon TD
videos.description: Travis Dye finds himself in space and into the end zone for the 11-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Travis Dye breaks through the hole for the Oregon TD) 2021/10/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cal gets huge turnover right before halftime
videos.description: Anthony Brown loses the football at midfield and Cal recovers as Oregon squanders an opportunity before the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cal gets huge turnover right before halftime) 2021/10/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Reinwald gives Cal lead after running over defender for TD
videos.description: Cal's Gavin Reinwald goes right through the Oregon defense for the 4-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Reinwald gives Cal lead after running over defender for TD) 2021/10/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Anthony Brown threads needle to Jaylon Redd for Oregon TD
videos.description: Oregon ties the game after Anthony Brown throws a dart to Jaylon Redd for the 20-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Anthony Brown threads needle to Jaylon Redd for Oregon TD) 2021/10/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Anthony Brown goes full extension towards pylon for TD run
videos.description: Oregon quarterback Anthony Brown leaps for the pylon and gets the touchdown, giving Oregon the late lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Anthony Brown goes full extension towards pylon for TD run) 2021/10/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon gets huge fourth-down stop to win the game
videos.description: Oregon gets the fourth down stop from inside their own 5 as they hold on to avoid the upset.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Oregon gets huge fourth-down stop to win the game) 2021/10/15 ESHEET
